#This is just a text file
x<- 1:50 
plot(x,sin(x))

#type l is line
plot(x,sin(x),typ="l")

#col is color
plot(x,sin(x),typ="l", col="blue")

#lwd makes the lines thicker
plot(x,sin(x),typ="l", col="blue", lwd=2)

plot(x,sin(x),typ="l", col="blue", lwd=2, xlab="hello")
